Package application

Class Parttime

java.lang.Object
application.Employee
application.Parttime
public class Parttime
extends Employee
The parttime class is one of the subclasses of the Employee superclass. It defines the components of an employee that works at a company parttime. It is responsible for obtaining and setting the hourly rate of a parttime employee as well as calculating what they earn for the current pay period.
Author:
Ceceliachollette-Dickson, Nidaansari
